    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>Muttering a short invocation and pointing at your target, you send a bolt of fire streaking forward.</em></p><p><strong>Spell Attack</strong> </p><p>If this spell damages a vehicle or object that is flammable and has hit points, the object is set on fire**.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> [[/damage 1d12 fire]] damage*</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Using Higher Level Spell Slots:</strong> This spell's damage increases by 1d12 when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d12 fire]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d12 fire]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d12 fire]]).</p><p>**Some objects may be too large or flammable to be simply extinguished as an action, and will require creative solutions. Additionally, some vehicles or other objects may have a 'damage threshold'. For example, a fire bolt would have to deal at least 5 damage to damage and ignite a wooden catapult. Once ignited, the ignited object takes [[/damage 1d10 fire]] damage at the end of each of the caster's turns, which is dealt regardless of the target's damage threshold.</p>",
            "chat": "<strong>Spell Attack</strong> </p><p>If this spell damages a vehicle or object that is flammable and has hit points, the object is set on fire**.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> [[/damage 1d12 fire]] damage*</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Using Higher Level Spell Slots:</strong> This spell's damage increases by 1d12 when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d12 fire]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d12 fire]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d12 fire]]).</p><p>**Some objects may be too large or flammable to be simply extinguished as an action, and will require creative solutions. Additionally, some vehicles or other objects may have a 'damage threshold'. For example, a fire bolt would have to deal at least 5 damage to damage and ignite a wooden catapult. Once ignited, the ignited object takes [[/damage 1d10 fire]] damage at the end of each of the caster's turns, which is dealt regardless of the target's damage threshold.</p>"
